@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = 0.50
    v1 = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.16 / v2 + 0.16) - (tmp + 0.48 / tmp + 0.56)))
    v2 = ((0.42 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.72)) - wp.sin((v0 + 0.49 * v0 + 0.23)))
    data[tid] = v0
